      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:22:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场总结：多数亚洲股市因对特朗普胜选的担忧而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡特朗普连任总统将对市场产生的影响（承诺提高关税），亚洲股市多数下跌。美元在周三上涨逾 1% 后小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:21:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选重创全球降息预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-win-wreaks-havoc-with-rate-cut-expectations-around-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 强势重返美国总统大位后，世界各地的央行行长们都在判断，他们最担心的事情是否会成为现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-win-wreaks-havoc-with-rate-cut-expectations-around-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 16:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管 60% 的关税可能带来混乱，但习近平已为应对特朗普做好了更充分的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/xi-is-better-prepared-for-trump-even-as-60-tariffs-risk-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2018 年，当唐纳德·特朗普首次与中国发起贸易战时，北京发现自己处于劣势，不知道该如何应对。这一次，习近平主席做好了更充分的准备，尽管他可能会失去更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/xi-is-better-prepared-for-trump-even-as-60-tariffs-risk-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:45:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
